           if        rf-ocr-flg-puq       not  = "K"
                     go to det-age-mic-542.
           divide    1000                 into rf-ocr-qta-ord
                                        giving w-qta-dev-qta-dew      .
           multiply  w-qta-dev-qta-dew    by   rf-ocr-prz-net
                                        giving w-det-imp-res-ipr      .
           go to     det-age-mic-543.
       det-age-mic-542.
           multiply  rf-ocr-qta-ord       by   rf-ocr-prz-net
                                        giving w-det-imp-res-ipr      .
           go to     det-age-mic-543.
       det-age-mic-543.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Eventuale aggiustamento con decimali    *
